Client Services ManagerLinda acts as our Client Service Manager and serves as a primary point of contact for clients with our firm for administrative and service-oriented needs. She handles scheduling, oversees client administrative needs, works with our corporate retirement plan administrators, and helps coordinate solutions for client insurance needs. She has been a long-time valued staff member of TMD and tends to be the “go-to” person for most of our clients. Linda attended the University of Phoenix and received her BS degree in Business and Information Systems. Linda is an active volunteer to a local veteran organization, participating in several Arizona StandDown events (annual events to aid and assist homeless veterans). She is also a proud grandmother.


