Steven Neeley, MBA

This e-mail address is being protected from spambots. You need JavaScript enabled to view it
 




Financial and Retirement Planning SpecialistAlso a CFP® professional, Steven is actively involved in the preparation of our financial plans, is a member of the investment committee, and provides extensive support and analysis of our investments. He also handles employee education, enrollment, and technical follow-up for our retirement plans. Steven grew up in Indiana and received his BA from Indiana University, followed by an MBA from the Thunderbird School of Global Management. Utilizing his ability to speak Mandarin Chinese, Steven lived and worked in Taiwan for five years prior to moving to Arizona. As a result, he follows trends in international business and capital markets very closely, particularly in Asia. During his time abroad, Steven met his wife, Julia. Along with chasing after their young son, Aiden, they enjoy seeking out the best dim sum Arizona has to offer.


Primary Duties at TMD

Acts as your primary contact for research, investment due diligence, and trading
Oversees analyses and portfolion construction to provide you with the best in-class wealth management
Monitors the market for potential impact on your investments






 



Susan Abbass, MBA

