Operations ManagerSusan is responsible for day-to-day oversight of TMD’s operations. She oversees TMD’s compliance program, handles due-diligence issues for alternative assets, and coordinates TMD’s in-office workflow processes. She holds a BA from Bucknell University and an MBA from Pace University in Manhattan. Prior to joining TMD, Susan lived in New York City and worked for a decade on Wall Street for a foreign investment bank. She got her start in business at the US Headquarters for Davidoff of Geneva, a Swiss importer of fine cigars and luxury goods. Susan speaks fluent German, is an active triathlete, and loves spending time with her two young boys.


