TMD & Associates, Inc. | Financial Planners, Investment Advisors, Portfolio Managers located in Phoenix, AZ




































Saturday, 22 July 2017

TDA LoginJoin MeetingDocument VaultFAQADVPrivacy







































 Financial Planning ServicesWealth Management ServicesCorporate SolutionsExecutive Solutions












Personalized Wealth Management
Our Firm provides comprehensive fee-based wealth management services to business owners, corporate executives, professional athletes, and similarly affluent clients. We utilize a team approach in analyzing and planning our client’s investment portfolio, estate plan, cash flow, income taxes, and retirement. The firm is registered with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. We require our advisors to be CERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER™ licensees, ensuring that our clients receive knowledgeable, unbiased advice. TMD also recognizes the need for individual recommendations based solely on specific needs, circumstances, and goals; our clients count on us to stay on top of the ever-changing ‘face’ and unknowns of the market, its politics, and its people.  





About TMD





Our Core Belief OUR CORE BELIEF is to provide our clients with the highest level of service and technical expertise in the management and preservation of wealth. The entire staff of TMD & Associates is firmly committed to this philosophy so that we can make a difference in our client's lives.
Learn more 



Our Objective OUR OBJECTIVE is to provide our clients with the financial "peace of mind" that they need to fully enjoy their lives. We will do this by using the financial planning process as a means to help them organize, prioritize, and realize their financial goals and dreams. Our purpose is to help build, manage and preserve your wealth. We put our client's interest first, act with integrity and honesty, and strive for excellence in every facet of our practice. Our success is not measured by performance statistics but rather by our clients' success in achieving their goals.
Learn more 



Your Goals, Our Solutions OUR CLIENTS share in the realization that by coordinating and managing today's financial decisions, they can achieve their goals for tomorrow. They are individuals and businesses who expect excellence and have made a firm commitment to achieving it themselves. Our clients usually have no desire to manage their financial affairs on a daily basis, want to simplify their lives, and are willing to enter into a long-term relationship that is mutually beneficial. They are highly motivated to work with a professional advisor, not a sales representative.
Learn more 



Partnering with Others for a Better Result Our firm recognizes that our clients' needs are best served by a teamwork approach, so we partner with other professionals whose deep knowledge spans across a great range of specialties. This way, our clients are kept informed without having to manage the daily workflow of wealth management. For those clients who already have trusted relationships with other advisors, we will work with both you and your advisors to assure that we develop a coordinated plan that meets your personal needs.
Learn more
  













Chains of habit are too light to be felt until they are too heavy to be broken.       -- Warren Buffett

